# 🔗 Job Triggering & Notification Flow

```text
Job 1: Create File
       ↓
Job 2: Publish File Content
       ↓
Slack & Email Notifications

Key Features Implemented
Git automation via Jenkins Freestyle Job
File creation & content management
Automated job triggering (Job 2 after Job 1)
Slack & Email notifications for failures and successes
Freestyle job configuration for easy reproducibility
📌 Conclusion

This assignment demonstrates:

Building Freestyle Jobs for automation
Managing Git operations from Jenkins
Implementing dependency between jobs
Enabling Slack & Email notifications for CI monitoring
Publishing files to a web server in an automated and structured
